WEBVTT

00:00:07.902 --> 00:00:10.772
Fine day, Sunday.

00:00:11.406 --> 00:00:16.068
In my opinion, best day of the week.
Why is that, Dudley?

00:00:16.286 --> 00:00:20.699
- Because there's no post on Sundays?
- Right you are, Harry!

00:00:20.915 --> 00:00:23.666
No post on Sunday.

00:00:25.086 --> 00:00:29.000
No blasted letters today! No, sir.

00:00:29.590 --> 00:00:34.548
Not one single bloody letter. Not one!

